# === git-exposure-guardian (2026-06-22): never commit secrets / internal assets ===
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
*.pem
*.key
*.p12
*.pfx
*.p8
*.keystore
*.jks
id_rsa*
id_ed25519*
*-credentials.json
*credentials*.json
serviceAccount*.json
gcp-*.json
firebase-adminsdk*.json
.dev.vars
.wrangler/
secrets/
_docs/
research_bus/
MEMORY.md
*.local
# === end git-exposure-guardian ===
